	`w3m-modeline-process-status-on' when process running.
	(w3m-download): Add 4th argument `extview' for
	w3m-external-view(). If `extview' is gived, apply `extview' on
	process-sentinel like (apply (car extview) (cdr extview)).
	(w3m-external-view): When execute `w3m-download', call with
	`extview' argument.
	(w3m-external-view-file): New function.

