	(w3m-detect-coding-region): New function.

	* w3m-om.el (coding-system-category): Removed.
	(w3m-detect-coding-region): New function.

	* w3m-fsf.el: New file.

	* w3m-form.el (w3m-form-default-coding-system): Abolished.
